Introducing layouts, forms, mail, marketplace and automations ( https://www.notion.so?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Hi Emil,

I think this may be our largest release ever?!

We’ve just shipped forms, automations, layouts, a new Marketplace, custom emojis, and a sneak peek of Notion Mail! The team has worked really hard to bring you these features, and we hope they make it faster and easier than ever to get things done—all in one tool.

Try new features ( https://www.notion.so/?mwn2024=true&utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Notion Mail (coming soon!)

Email hasn’t changed in 20 years. It's cluttered, chaotic, and hard to manage. So we rebuilt it! Notion Mail is fast, minimal, and does all the organizing and back-and-forth of scheduling for you! Best part is “views” that let you customize your inbox to your workflows, just like the rest of Notion. We can’t wait for you to try the preview and hear how it changes the way you work. Join the waitlist! ( https://www.notion.so/product/mail?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Notion Mail preview ( https://www.notion.so/?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Introducing forms, right inside Notion!

Forms give you an easy way to capture the info you need—from your personal trackers to RSVPs, surveys, and signup forms you can share with others! Responses are stored in a Notion database, where you can keep everything organized and visualize data in a chart. No need for an outside tool! The best part is you get unlimited forms for
free. Try one out → ( https://notion.so/?target=create_form&utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Forms within Notion ( https://notion.so/?target=create_form&utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Layouts to customize your page

Your work is unique and your tools should be flexible enough to match! So we created a way for you to further customize your goals, documents, or whatever you keep in Notion. Layouts bring more beauty and creativity to pages! Try it out by hovering over any database page title and clicking Customize layout.

Layouts to customize your page ( https://www.notion.so/?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Introducing the new Marketplace

Have you created an amazing setup or workflow? We’ve made it easier than ever to list and sell your template. Native payments, analytics, reviews and ratings, safeguards to prevent unfair re-distribution—all in the best place for millions of users to discover your work! Whether you’re looking for the perfect template or starting a business—there are creators who make seven figures on Notion!—this is the place. Go to Marketplace → ( https://www.notion.so/templates?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Notion marketplace ( https://www.notion.so/templates?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Custom emojis!

Maybe the best update ever? You can now upload your own emojis! Use them in your page titles or anywhere—just type /emoji or : followed by its name. Our favorite is :bufo-thumbs-up: :bufo-thumbsup: .

Custom emojis ( https://www.notion.so/?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Personalize your URLs

Notion Site URLs often have a long string of numbers and characters, but now you can make them exactly what you’d like! Cory, our video producer and resident birder, turned his site birdingnyc.com/My-spotted-birds-1c7d9d506ecf4802b686839e8ddc9909 into birdingnyc.com/mybirds. Just use the Share → Publish menu. This will be rolling out to everyone in the coming weeks. If you don't see it yet, you will soon. Learn more → ( https://www.notion.so/help/manage-your-notion-sites?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Personalize URLs ( https://www.notion.so/?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Automate more actions with formulas

This is a true superpower. Database and button automations now support formulas that can complete steps in the background when you trigger an action—a huge timesaver. For example, when you mark a task done, you can automatically show how little time it took to complete. Dig in to learn more → ( https://www.notion.so/help/database-automations?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io#database-automation-actions )

Automations now support formulas ( https://www.notion.so/?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Automations can now send emails

Now you can use an automation to notify people via Gmail (one of your top requests!). Trigger an email when information changes, like when a form has been submitted or the status of a task changes. Soon you’ll be able to send custom web requests to platforms like Zapier and Make to trigger actions in other apps, too.

Automations to notify people via email ( https://www.notion.so/?utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

Shortcut to Notion features

When searching, type in a keyword like “Home,” “Settings,” or “Templates” to jump to specific places in Notion. Try it with the ⌘ P keyboard shortcut. It’s a small thing that can make you much
faster!

Notion mail ( https://notion.so/?target=quickfind&utm_campaign=What%27s+New+2.46+-+Reactivation&utm_campaigntype=behavioral&utm_content=Catchall+-+L90+%3C+L180&utm_medium=email&utm_source=customer.io )

